==發行==
華納兄弟公司原定将影片于2016年5月6日上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pedersen|first1=Erik|title=Warner Bros Dates Catnapping Pic ‘Keanu’ & ‘Going In Style’ Remake For 2016|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/keanu-release-date-going-in-style-key-and-peele-morgan-freeman-michael-caine-1201433439/|accessdate=August 4, 2015|work=deadline.com|date=May 27, 2015|archive-date=2016-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102152856/http://deadline.com/2015/05/keanu-release-date-going-in-style-key-and-peele-morgan-freeman-michael-caine-1201433439/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但上映日期最终被推迟至2017年4月7日<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Warner Bros. Shifts Release Dates For ‘The Accountant’, ‘Going In Style’ & ‘The House’|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-accountant-going-in-style-the-house-release-date-changes-1201716752/|accessdate=March 10, 2016|work=Deadline|date=March 8, 2016|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310110518/http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-accountant-going-in-style-the-house-release-date-changes-1201716752/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
《瀟灑搶一回》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於97條評論，新鮮度46%，平均得分5.3／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/going_in_style_2017 |title=Going in Style (2017) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=Fandango |accessdate=April 6, 2017 |archive-date=2017-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127152335/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/going_in_style_2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了50分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/going-in-style |title=Going in Style reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=April 6, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407074718/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/going-in-style |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-09-13 |archive-date=2002-09-14 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20020914132118/https://www.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
《三个老枪手》在美国和加拿大取得4500万美元的票房，并在海外则取得3990万美元票房，合计票房收入接近8500万美元。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=goinginsty2017.htm |title="Going in Style (2017)". Box Office Mojo |accessdate=September 22, 2019 |archive-date=2018-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005185316/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=goinginsty2017.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

北美地区的首日票房为420万美元，第一个周末票房达到1190万美元，票房成绩高于预期，位列本周票房榜第四名。<ref name=opening>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/04/smurfs-the-lost-village-going-in-style-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-box-office-1202064314/ |title='Boss Baby' Crawls Ahead Of 'Beauty' With $26M+; 'Smurfs' Lost In 3rd With $14M |work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |accessdate=April 9, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409180408/http://deadline.com/2017/04/smurfs-the-lost-village-going-in-style-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-box-office-1202064314/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第二周周末票房为630万美元（下降了47%），位列票房榜第五名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/04/16/box-office-ghost-in-the-shell-power-rangers-stumble-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-hold/ |title=Box Office: 'Ghost In The Shell,' 'Power Rangers' Stumble, 'Boss Baby,' 'Beauty And The Beast' Hold |date=April 16, 2017 |publisher=Forbes |accessdate=2019-09-22 |archive-date=2017-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419004617/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/04/16/box-office-ghost-in-the-shell-power-rangers-stumble-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-hold/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

